                        <div id="page-title">
                            Jonnesh研究员与Alexy特工于2019年2月4日的聊天记录
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+32</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoHolder" style="display:inline-block; width:100%;">
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDiv" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: #73AD21;padding: 15px;width: 100px; height: 25px;display: inline-block">
<p>在吗？</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-314010021922961950" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 25px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>怎么了Jonney？</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-10431601951114466716" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDiv" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: #73AD21;padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 75px;display: inline-block">
<p>太累了……真的太累了Ale……太累了……我已经四天没连续睡过2个小时的觉了……</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-1584299479673872741" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">DOWN</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-6846404641645290626" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 125px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>习惯就好Jonney，你知道的，基金会从来不给闲人提供工作，进来了就会忙死。你看我们，这些干场外特工的，基本上和那些刀尖舔血的抢劫犯的工作难度一样了。只不过我们的报酬少一点。</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-10049561631507343415" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">DOWN</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-11226168191938488734" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDiv" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: #73AD21;padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 200px;display: inline-block">
<p>不知道什么时候起工作数量以及不是按照几张文件计算了……之前还是按照几厘米的文件……就在上个星期开始已经是按照几公斤文件来工作了。这样的工作强度真的受不了，每一次这种强度工作就是要完成一份收容措施的新工程，一年两个工程，一个工程时间是6个月……我真的快累死了。</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-23029747431423123" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">DOWN</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-1092015842090543216" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDiv" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: #73AD21;padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 125px;display: inline-block">
<p>我想辞职，这可能是我最好的选择，一份报告书，六个月清除全部工作，一粒五级记忆清除药剂，什么事情全部忘在脑后，出去找一份好工作，安逸得很</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-11064677891614769378" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">DOWN</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-7874952451976546782" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 100px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>想开点吧Jonney，努力朝前看，年纪轻轻要什么安逸……别想着辞职了，基金会福利很好啊，去年的新政策多么好，我能省下很多很多钱！</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-7837276521438123258" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">&#8230;&#8230;.</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-1121390447223293319" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 125px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>就那个《基金会基层员工家庭保障政策》，保证每一个基金会工作人员的家庭成员的健康，我操这政策也太棒了，我爸治病的钱一直全部报销，虽然不是基金会那种高级治疗，但是也是好医院了。</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-18461115721980342817" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">UP</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-7921590271868662903" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 75px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>这个太他妈的不错了……我爱死这个政策了。对了jonney，我记得你不也是家里有病人嘛？</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-316901735321017225" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDiv" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: #73AD21;padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 125px;display: inline-block">
<p>嗯对，我妈癌症，快扩散了……不过不知道为啥，她一直没扩散，四次病危通知书了，还活着。还有我哥哥，白血病，但是一直接受治疗，治好的可能性还挺大。</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-1176548059348302737" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">DOWN</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-9649552872224607" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 100px; height: 125px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>肯定啊，你父母在75岁之前不能死，基金会不会让你家里人过早的死，过早会引起周围人的注意。</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-14627694531680795007" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 100px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>对啊，你看，你更不能辞职了，你一走你就不属于政策管辖范围之内了，你家里人是死是活基金会就不管了，你一走你家里人必死啊！</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-7460973482147409917" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 75px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>所以，千万不能辞职，不只是为了你，更为了你家里人，你的努力全是给你家里人的幸福。</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-11786019851751053511" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe><br />
<span style="color: white">UP</span></p>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-1507269684153735157" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 175px; height: 75px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>压力太大了，我帮你请个假？忙过去这一阵子你可以休息休息，基金会休假都是带薪的，累了这么久你是该休息休息了。</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-15420585971530299432" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDiv" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: #73AD21;padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 25px;display: inline-block">
<p>谢谢你……不必了</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-5851582801651260182" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDiv" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: #73AD21;padding: 15px;width: 150px; height: 50px;display: inline-block">
<p>我等会去洗个澡休息一下就行……谢谢你了</p>
</div>
<p><iframe src="/resignation/html/30249b1ce4d19bf17ea8834babcca213212116c0-14733590001691626069" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div id="u-myTextMessageConvoDivReply" style="color:white; border-radius: 25px; background: blue; padding: 15px;width: 75px; height: 75px;float:right; display: inline-block">
<p>嗯，加油，改天我请你吃饭。</p>
</div>
</div>

